flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 32: Weather-Aware Demand Signal Pipeline and Feature Injection

  Cron[Daily CRON at 6 AM\nBangladesh time]
  Fetch[Call OpenWeatherMap 5-day API]
  FetchOK{Fetch successful?}

  Derive[Derive weather features\ntemperature_avg\nprecipitation_mm\nis_monsoon]
  Persist[(Update weather_cache)]
  Cache[Write Redis cache\nTTL 6h]

  ImpactMatrix[Apply category impact matrix\nMonsoon: rain gear up\nOutdoor demand down]
  Inject[Inject weather features into\nForecast and ROP modules]

  UseStale{Recent cached weather available?}
  FallbackCache[Use last valid cached weather\nMark stale-data flag]
  Degrade[Use neutral weather defaults\nMark stale-data and lower confidence]
  Alert[Emit observability alert]

  Cron --> Fetch --> FetchOK
  FetchOK -- Yes --> Derive --> Persist --> Cache --> ImpactMatrix --> Inject

  FetchOK -- No --> UseStale
  UseStale -- Yes --> FallbackCache --> ImpactMatrix --> Inject
  UseStale -- No --> Degrade --> Alert --> ImpactMatrix --> Inject
